description: Dry ice was poured into the baths at an Instagram influencer's birthday party, media reports say.
title: Three die in dry-ice incident at Moscow pool party
title_page: Three die in dry-ice incident at Moscow pool party - BBC News
maintext: In an earlier video message, the blogger, looking shaken and distressed, said he had been been rushed to intensive care. All the victims are said to be aged about 30.
